2016年6月13日，[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]全票通过343號决议案，关注和谴责中国共产党[[活体摘除|活体摘除]]法轮功学员器官，要求中国共产党立即停止迫害法轮功，要求[[美国国务院|美国国务院]]每年向国会汇报，禁止中国共产党活摘参与人员进入美国的2003年国务院授权法案(8 U.S.C. 1182f)的执行状况。<ref name="congress.gov">{{cite news|title=H.Res.343 - Expressing concern regarding persistent and credible reports of systematic, state-sanctioned organ harvesting from non-consenting prisoners of conscience in the People's Republic of China, including from large numbers of Falun Gong practitioners and members of other religious and ethnic minority groups.|date=2016-06-13|url=https://www.congress.gov/bill/114th-congress/house-resolution/343/text|work=美国国会|language=en|accessdate=2016-11-17|archive-date=2016-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122222318/https://www.congress.gov/bill/114th-congress/house-resolution/343/text|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年7月，歐洲議會以絕大多數票通過〈48/2016書面聲明〉決議，稱「有持續可靠的報導表明，在中國存在政府批准的系統性對良心犯器官的活摘，未經當事人同意。其中主要受害者是那些和平的法輪功修煉者，以及維吾爾族、藏族人和基督徒。」諸此不法行為的嚴重性「迫切需要立即對中国共产党持續的人體器官貿易進行獨立調查。」議員稱死亡人數涉及150萬人。<ref>{{cite news|title=Geschäfte des Grauens Im Europaparlament wurde erneut eine Resolution gegen Organraub in China initiiert|url=http://www.die-tagespost.de/aus-aller-welt/aus-aller-welt/Geschaefte-des-Grauens;art309,171349|agency={{link-de|每日郵報_德國|Die_Tagespost}}|date=2016-07-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818020413/http://www.die-tagespost.de/aus-aller-welt/aus-aller-welt/Geschaefte-des-Grauens;art309,171349|archivedate=2016-08-18|accessdate=2016-11-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 媒體宣傳戰 ===
中国政府對法輪功的镇压，是以大規模宣傳來驅動，包括電視、報紙、廣播與網路。<ref name="Tong2009"/><ref name="Leung" />在镇压发生的一个月内，中国国内的每一家主要官方媒體都发表了300-400篇文章攻击法轮功，中国的电视台在黄金时间节目重播对法轮功的指控，其没有任何不同於政府的看法觀點。<ref name="lemish">Leeshai Lemish, [http://www.cesnur.org/2009/slc_lemish.htm "Media and New Religious Movements: The Case of Falun Gong"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cesnur.org/2009/slc_lemish.htm |date=20150418053706 }}, A paper presented at The 2009 CESNUR Conference, Salt Lake City, Utah, 11–13 June 2009</ref>这场宣传戰（propaganda campaign），集中指控法轮功影响社会稳定、具欺骗性和危险性、威胁社会进步，並稱法轮功的伦理哲学不相容於马克思主义的社会伦理观。<ref name="ownbyfuture"/>其他官員稱將是一個“長期，複雜和嚴重的”鬥爭“剷除”法輪功。<ref>Plafker, Ted. "Falun Gong Stays Locked In Struggle With Beijing," The Washington Post, 26 April 2000</ref>

西方学者Daniel Wright和Joseph Fewsmith提到，在法轮功于7月22日被宣布为非法后，中国[[中国中央电视台|中央电视台]]每晚半小时的[[新闻联播|新闻联播]]，从头至尾渲染反法轮功，在节目中专家、前法轮功练习者、普通居民纷纷发言指控法轮功欺骗信徒、分离家庭、损害健康、影响社会稳定；除此之外，晚间新闻几乎没有其他内容；对此，这两位学者认为：“这种政府操作完全是在妖魔化的分析”<ref name="Wright2003">{{cite book|author=Daniel B. Wright|title=The Promise of Revolution: Stories of Fulfillment and Struggle in China's Hinterland|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=0NPOPRUdE34C&pg=PA156|accessdate=2012-12-26|year=2003|publisher=Rowman & Littlefield|isbn=978-0-7425-1916-9|pages=156|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315053703/http://books.google.com/books?id=0NPOPRUdE34C&pg=PA156|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

政府舉國性的宣傳，最初訴諸於科學理性唯理，稱法輪功的世界觀是“完全反科學和反共產主義”<ref name=Lu2004>Lu, Xing, ''Rhetoric of the Chinese Cultural Revolution: the impact on Chinese thought, culture, and communication,'' University of South Carolina Press (2004).</ref>。例如，黨媒《[[人民日報|人民日報]]》1999年7月27日聲稱，對法輪功的鬥爭“是一個[[有神論|有神論]]和[[無神論|無神論]]、迷信和科學、唯心主義和[[唯物論|唯物主義]]之爭“。其他社論則宣稱法輪功的“唯心論（idealism）和有神論”都是與“馬克思主義基本理論原則的絕對矛盾”，並稱法輪功真、善、忍的原則”與我們努力實現的社會主義倫理及文化的進步沒有任何共同之處”。鎮壓法輪功，被呈現為是一項必要步驟，藉以維護共產黨在中國社會的“排頭兵（vanguard role）”角色。<ref>Chen, Chiung Hwang. "Framing Falun Gong: Xinhua News Agency's Coverage of the New Religious Movement in China", Asian Journal of Communication, Vol. 15 No. 1 (2005), pp. 16–36.</ref>

=== 轉折點：天安門自焚事件 ===
{{main|天安門自焚事件}}
2001年1月22日，[[法新社|法新社]]發表〈中国因镇压法轮功失败而惊恐〉報導，稱18个月来的镇压中，法輪功學員未屈服、而变得更坚定；并提及中国共产党领导层对江泽民的镇压有很大分歧，许多领导人表态反对镇压。香港學者刘苏凯說：“江应为下令镇压负主要责任，镇压运动毫无结果，江将政府逼入死角。事后看来，镇压非常鲁莽和轻率，尤其是在中国正努力在世界上重塑形象的时候。江骑虎难下。这涉及到他个人权力的问题。他担心如果给他们一点呼吸的空间，他就会被党内看做软弱，而无法保持最高领导地位”。<ref>{{cite web|title=China Spooked by Failure to Crush Falungong|first=|last=|date=2000-01-22 |work=AFP|language=en|publisher= |page=}}{{quote| China's leadership is increasingly alarmed and divided by the failure of its campaign to destroy the Falungong as it braces for new protests on the eve of the Spring Festival. For 18 months the spiritual movement has weathered an all-out assault, and despite the violent suppression of peaceful protests it still gathers hundreds of followers in Beijing's Tiananmen Square to mark key dates. In a surprising admission of failure, China said earlier this month it had been unable to prevent hundreds of Falungong members protesting daily in the square. There is a major split within the senior leadership. There are many leaders who are voicing disagreement with the crackdown."Jiang bears the major responsibility for ordering the crackdown," said Professor Lau Siu-kai of the Chinese University in Hong Kong. "The move has not borne fruit and Jiang has pushed the government into a corner. With hindsight it looks rash and over-confident, particularly as China is trying to rebuild its image in the world," he said. Factions in government believe the violent suppression of protests are hurting China's image just as it battles to overcome the damaging legacy of the military's crushing of the 1989 pro-democracy movement. Frank Lu says the crackdown does not have strong support within the leadership."Jiang can't back down. It involves his power. He's afraid if he gives them a little breathing space, he'll look weak in front of the party and not strong enough to keep being a top leader," he said.}}</ref>

宣傳戰的轉折點，是2001年中國除夕1月23日，[[新華社|新華社]]通報有五人在天安門廣場試圖自焚。[[新華社|新華社]]等官媒宣稱，自焚者是法輪功學員，法輪大法信息中心反駁，称法輪功書籍明確禁止暴力行為與自殺<ref>{{cite journal|author1=Page|coauthors=Jeremy|title=Survivors say China Falungong inmmolations real|journal=Reuters|date=2002-04-04}}</ref>，並称整起事件為中国共产党江澤民政府自導自演，藉此引起群眾對法輪功的負面印象，以確立鎮壓合理性<ref name="FDI_PressRelease">{{Cite web|url=http://en.minghui.org/eng/2001/jan/23/vsf012301_3.html|title=PRESS STATEMENT|date=2001-01-31|author=Falun Dafa Information Center|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-24|quote=|archive-date=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015055709/http://en.minghui.org/eng/2001/jan/23/vsf012301_3.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://faluninfo.net/article/1114/?cid=84 |title=On Ten Year Anniversary, Tiananmen Square Self-Immolation Continues to Be Deadly Frame-up |publisher=Falun Dafa Information Center |date=2001-01-23 |language=en |accessdate=2013-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121127041155/http://faluninfo.net/article/1114/?cid=84 |archive-date=2012-11-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=brady08>Anne-Marie Brady, Marketing dictatorship: propaganda and thought work in contemporary China, Rowman & Littlefield, 2008</ref>。

國際媒體報道了此事件，焚燒的錄像後來在中國境內由[[中國中央電視台|中國中央電視台]]（CCTV）播出。一個12歲女孩形象，劉思影，與其他參與者接受採訪，說他們相信自焚會引導他們到天堂。<ref name="FDI_PressRelease"/><ref name=oneway>{{Cite news|first=Philip P. |last=Pan |url= |title=One-Way Trip to the End in Beijing |work=International Herald Tribune |date=2001-02-05|accessdate=2007-02-09}}</ref>但是，一名在現場目擊的CNN製片人說她在現場沒有看到自焚者有兒童。<ref name=GMJ />CNN報道指5名自焚者中至少2名男性、沒有小孩；但新華社卻稱自焚者只1名男性，而4名女性包括1名12歲女童劉思影，後來更改稱自焚者共有7人，其中2人「自焚未遂」。<ref name="Apple123"/>天安門廣場上自焚者的身份遭到[[美國有線電視新聞網|美國有線電視新聞網]]CNN製片人的質疑，製片人她當時就在現場，對於中国政府稱12歲的劉思影在母親的催促下進行自焚。她表示當時在現場並未看到自焚者中有兒童<ref name="Schechter2001"/>{{rp|22-23}}

法輪功人士和其他評論家指出，主要參與自焚者的陳述及其他方面的行為，都不符合法輪功的教導。<ref name=WOIPFG2>{{Cite web |url=http://www.zhuichaguoji.org/en/node/54 |title=New Evidence Confirms Alleged Falun Gong "Tiananmen Square Self-Immolation" Was a State Conspiracy |publisher=World Organization to Investigate the Persecution of Falun Gong |date=August 2004 |accessdate=2013-07-22 |archive-date=2013-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130325173957/http://www.zhuichaguoji.org/en/node/54 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>一些媒體和國際教育發展組織（IED）同意，所謂自焚事件是由中国政府導演以“證明”法輪功洗腦了其追隨者去自殺，因此應被視為對國家的威脅而被禁止。IED代表在第53屆聯合國會議上發言說，描述了政府以[[國家恐怖主義|國家恐怖主義]]行為對待法輪功學員，自焚事件“是由政府策劃導演的”。<ref name=GMJ>{{Cite web|url=http://lass.purduecal.edu/cca/gmj/fa05/graduatefa05/gmj-fa05gradinv-yang.htm|title=The Perfect Example of Political Propaganda: The Chinese Government's Persecution against Falun Gong|publisher=Global Media Journal (Volume 4, Issue 7)|date=Fall 2005|accessdate=2014-04-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20121215000947/http://lass.purduecal.edu/cca/gmj/fa05/graduatefa05/gmj-fa05gradinv-yang.htm|archivedate=2012-12-15}}</ref><ref name="IED">{{cite web|first=|last=|url=http://www.unhchr.ch/huricane/huricane.nsf/0/D1D7C610CB97B340C1256AA9002678B0?opendocument|title=Terrorism, Transnational Corporations, Traditional Practices Discussed|work=UNITED NATIONS（聯合國人權高級專員網站）|accessdate=2013-03-01|language=en|date=2001-08-14|archive-date=2013-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526181318/http://www.unhchr.ch/huricane/huricane.nsf/0/D1D7C610CB97B340C1256AA9002678B0?opendocument|dead-url=no}}{{quotation|KAREN PARKER, of International Educational Development, said State terrorism in the form of Government terror against its own people produced far more gross violations of human rights than any other form of terrorism; an example was China's treatment of the Falun Gong. The Government had sought to justify its terrorism against Falun Gong by calling it an evil cult that had caused deaths and the break-up of families, but the organization's investigation showed that the only deaths and resulting family breakups had been at the hands of Chinese authorities, who had resorted to extreme torture and unacceptable detention of thousands of people. International Educational Development had discovered that a self-immolation cited by the Chinese Government as proof that the Falun Gong was an evil cult in fact had been staged. The international community and the Subcommission should urgently address this situation.}}</ref>《華盛頓郵報》記者菲利普·潘寫道，兩名自焚死亡者實際上不是法輪功學員。<ref>Pan, Philip P. (5 February 2001). "One-Way Trip to the End in Beijing". International Herald Tribune.</ref>2001年3月21日，當劉思影很有活力地被以為將出醫院回家時，卻突然死亡。<ref name=GMJ />
<ref name="RFA20010317">{{cite news |url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/52532-20010317.html |title=The Breaking Point |work=[[自由亚洲电台|RFA]] |date=2001-03-17 |accessdate=2020-01-20 |archive-date=2020-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610212749/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/52532-20010317.html/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

中国政府在之后随即通过加大宣传力度来削弱公众对法轮功的亲和度。《[[时代|时代]]》杂志指出，许多中国人在以前并不觉得法轮功造成真正的威胁，認為政府的鎮壓與事實不符、反對政府的镇压政策；但在自焚事件后，随着政府官方媒体集中报导并批判法轮功后<ref name="Apple123"/><ref name="breakingpoint">{{cite news |first=Matthew |last=Forney |url=http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,165163,00.html |title=The Breaking Point |work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] |date=2001-06-25 |accessdate=2016-11-17 |archive-date=2007-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071013111614/http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,165163,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，民众开始对法轮功具有负面想法，各種批評法輪功的海報、傳單和視頻不斷被製作出來，各級學校定期安排「反法輪功」課程<ref name="Dangerous"/><ref name="oneway"/><ref name="chrandra">{{cite journal|first=Chrandra D.|last=Smith|url=http://org.law.rutgers.edu/publications/law-religion/new_devs/RJLR_ND_66.pdf|format=PDF|title=Chinese Persecution of Falun Gong|publisher=Rutgers School of Law|journal=Rutgers Journal of Law and Religion|date=October 2004|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090327075424/http://org.law.rutgers.edu/publications/law-religion/new_devs/RJLR_ND_66.pdf|archivedate=2009-03-27}}</ref>。CNN指出，政府在此次事件中的宣传措施，和以往的政治运动，诸如[[朝鲜战争|朝鲜战争]]和[[文化大革命|文化大革命]]等非常相像<ref name="tense">{{Cite web|url=http://archives.cnn.com/2001/WORLD/asiapcf/east/01/24/asia.falun.03/|title=Tiananmen tense after fiery protests|date=2001-01-24|publisher=CNN|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-24|quote=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070222110517/http://archives.cnn.com/2001/WORLD/asiapcf/east/01/24/asia.falun.03/|archivedate=2007-02-22}}</ref>。《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》形容中国共产党「用電視、報紙等媒體圖像轟炸」，《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》指政府藉此事件「系統地暴力鎮壓」法輪功<ref name="Apple123"/>。后来，随着公众支持和舆论导向远离法轮功，中国政府也使用更加暴力的手段对待法轮功学员<ref name="breaking">{{cite news|author=Philip Pan and John Pomfret|title=Torture is Breaking Falun Gong|newspaper=Washington Post|date=2001-08-05|URL=https://archive.is/xVexH|accessdate=2013-02-24|language=en|archive-date=2013-02-22|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130222050420/http://faluninfo.net/article/566/-i-Washington-Post-i-Torture-Is-Breaking-Falun-Gong/}}</ref>，更为严厉的监禁和酷刑，法轮功学员在被拘押期间的死亡人数明显上升。<ref name=Freedomhouse>Sarah Cook, Sarah (4 November 2013) [http://www.freedomhouse.org/blog/be-skeptical-official-story-tiananmen-car-crash "Be Skeptical of the Official Story on the Tiananmen Car Crash"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.freedomhouse.org/blog/be-skeptical-official-story-tiananmen-car-crash |date=20140503002409 }} Freedom House.</ref>中華民國[[立法院|國會]]2004年的決議中提及，中国共产党「發動全國宣傳機器，全面抹黑、污衊李洪志先生，故外界亦一再質疑，大陸政府一手炮製[[天安門自焚事件|天安門自焚案]]等事件，意圖挑起一般人民對法輪功的仇恨。」<ref name=LY2004>{{cite web | url=http://lis.ly.gov.tw/ttscgi/lgimg?@933302;0649;0651 | title=立法院公報 93卷33期 院會記錄（2004年決議全文-要求停止打壓法輪功） | work=[[立法院|立法院]]國會圖書館 | date=2004年6月 | accessdate=2016-11-17 | archive-date=2017-04-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170403191746/http://lis.ly.gov.tw/ttscgi/lgimg?@933302;0649;0651 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2001年2月-天安門自焚事件一個月後，江澤民召開了一次罕見的中央工作會議，強調持續反法輪功運動的重要性、黨高層的團結。在江的領導下，對法輪功的鎮壓成為中國政治風氣“維穩”的一部分—跟黨在1989年六四天安門事件期間所採用的說詞(rhetoric)非常雷同。江的指示在2001年度全國人大會議中被呼應，“滅絕法輪功”被與中國經濟發展連結(tie)在一起。<ref name=Dangerous/>儘管在全國性議程(agenda)上不太突出，對法輪功的迫害在江澤民退休後仍然持續，2008、2009年仍發生對法功持續而高度的“[[嚴打|嚴打]]”。政府於2010年發動為期三年的一波行動，試圖再強制“轉化”法輪功學員。<ref>Congressional Executive Commission on China, [http://www.cecc.gov/pages/virtualAcad/index.phpd?showsingle=154369&PHPSESSID=5fbbb671b469039d4ec2ae47774039bd "Communist Party Calls for Increased Efforts To "Transform" Falun Gong Practitioners as Part of Three-Year Campaign"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cecc.gov/pages/virtualAcad/index.phpd?showsingle=154369&PHPSESSID=5fbbb671b469039d4ec2ae47774039bd |date=20110622035126 }}, 22 March 2011.</ref>

中国法輪功学员为了抵抗中共的信息封锁，會在小額[[人民幣|人民幣]][[紙幣|紙幣]]上打印法輪功信息，再將印有法轮功信息的這些小額紙幣發回市場流通。這樣的紙幣在[[雲南省|雲南省]]和[[四川省|四川省]]尤其多。國內街頭也有人銷售包含法輪功信息的DVD影片。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scmp.com/article/668802/falun-gong-spreading-message-banknotes|title=Falun Gong spreading message on banknotes|publisher=South China Morning Post|date=2009-02-04|accessdate=2018-01-31|archive-date=2020-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610212653/https://www.scmp.com/article/668802/falun-gong-spreading-message-banknotes|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.asianews.it/news-en/Chinese-banknotes-with-%E2%80%9Chidden%E2%80%9D-Falun-Gong-messages-14394.html|title=Chinese banknotes with “hidden” Falun Gong messages|publisher=AsiaNews.it|year=2009|quote=The banned Falun Gong spiritual movement is  countering China's offical censorship by printing messages on real reminbi banknotes and putting them back into circulation...|accessdate=2018-01-31|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803154032/http://www.asianews.it/news-en/Chinese-banknotes-with-%E2%80%9Chidden%E2%80%9D-Falun-Gong-messages-14394.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>


=== 法輪功對迫害的回應 ===
{{main|對法輪功的迫害#鎮壓與反鎮壓之戰}}
[[File:Protesting_the_Persecution_of_Falun_Gong_in_Washington_DC.jpg|缩略图]]

法輪功學員對中国共产党迫害的回應，先是向地方、省、中央各級政府持續依法[[上訪|上訪]]請願<ref>Elisabeth Rosenthal and Erik Eckholm, "Vast Numbers of Sect Members Keep Pressure on Beijing" New York Times, 28 October 1999.</ref>。這很快地發展擴大，每天都有數以百計的學員前往北京[[天安門廣場|天安門廣場]]展示功法、舉起橫幅以捍衛信仰；相關的學員很快遭到中国國安人員抓捕、有時被暴力地關押，截至2000年4月25日（425上訪一週年）就有逾30,000名學員遭抓捕<ref name="johnson2000">{{Cite web |url=http://www.pulitzer.org/archives/6464 |title=Defiant Falun Dafa Members Converge on Tiananmen |first=Ian |last=Johnson |date=2000-04-25 |work=The Wall Street Journal |publisher=Pulitzer.org |page=A21 |accessdate=2012-12-28 |archive-date=2009-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091229022658/http://www.pulitzer.org/archives/6464 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2001年7月1日一天就有700名學員在天安門廣場被抓捕<ref name="Perry">{{Cite book|first=Elizabeth J. |last=Selden |author2=Perry, Mark |title=Chinese Society: Change, Conflict and Resistance |publisher=Routledge |year=2003 |isbn=0-415-30170-X}}</ref>，這樣的公開抗議一直持續到2001年。普立茲奖得主记者[[张彦_(美国记者)|张彦]]（Ian Johnson）表示，（在受到镇压后）法轮功学员维护自己信仰的努力可能形成了50年来对共产党统治的最大挑战。<ref>Johnson, Ian. "A Deadly Exercise: Practicing Falun Gong was a right, Ms. Chen said, to her last day", Wall Street Journal, 20 April 2000.</ref>

2001年底，法轮功学员在天安门广场的公开呼吁不再频繁，转向在民间向民众「讲真相」。他们建立了较隐蔽的「资料点」制作传单和DVD等反击官方媒体对法轮功的描绘，然后向民众挨家挨户发送这些材料。<ref>Liao Yiwu. "The Corpse Walker: Real Life Stories: China from the Bottom Up." p 230.</ref>法轮功消息来源估计，至2009年，在中国有超过20万这种资料点的存在。<ref>Falun Dafa Information Center, "2010 Annual Report: Falun Gong Beliefs and Demography of Practitioners". 26 April 2010</ref>制作、持有或发送这些资料，经常是公安对法轮功学员监禁或判刑的理由。<ref>Congressional Executive Commission on China, 2009 Annual Report,[http://www.cecc.gov/pages/annualRpt/annualRpt09/CECCannRpt2009.pdf CECC report] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cecc.gov/pages/annualRpt/annualRpt09/CECCannRpt2009.pdf |date=20091103235417 }}</ref>

2002年，長春的法輪功學員以劫持方法將官方媒體的節目替換爲《法轮大法洪传世界》、《是自焚还是骗局》等法輪功方面製作的影片，{{citation needed|当地民众因此误以为镇压法轮功已经停止而聚集在廣場慶祝。事发后三天内，被上级嚴厲警告的长春政府，在全城搜捕了约2000-5000名當地学员，参与插播的刘成军等6人被先后暴打、酷刑折磨至死。由於正逢2001年初官營电视长时间渲染恐怖的[[天安门自焚事件|天安门自焚事件]]，導致中国民众自镇压初期「对法轮功学员的普遍同情正在消失」，6名插播者希望民众能從不一样的角度来看自焚事件}}<ref name=ws-20101206>{{cite news|last=Gutmann|first=Ethan|title=Into Thin Airwaves|url=http://www.weeklystandard.com/articles/thin-airwaves_519589.html?nopager=1|newspaper=The Weekly Standard|date=2010-12-06|accessdate=2016-11-17|archive-date=2012-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120105190542/http://www.weeklystandard.com/articles/thin-airwaves_519589.html?nopager=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=mediacontrol>{{cite book|title=The Fog of Censorship: Media Control in China|year=2008|publisher=Human Rights in China|isbn=978-0-9717356-2-0|pages=xii|url=http://hrichina.org/sites/default/files/oldsite/PDFs/Reports/HRIC-Fog-of-Censorship.pdf|author=He Qinglian|authorlink=何清漣|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229083633/http://hrichina.org/sites/default/files/oldsite/PDFs/Reports/HRIC-Fog-of-Censorship.pdf|archivedate=2012-02-29|access-date=2016-07-05}}</ref>。

北京政府運用中國境內的官方媒體抵制法輪功。{{citation needed|打压初期，国际媒體也大量轉載了中国大陆媒體的報導。}}中国政府在鎮壓後，也將法輪功設為敏感詞並在中國大陸境內屏蔽包含其內容的諸多網站。<ref name=Ownby08future/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://cyber.law.harvard.edu/filtering/china/|title=Empirical Analysis of Internet Filtering in China|website=cyber.law.harvard.edu|accessdate=2010-05-24|archive-date=2015-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150515143108/http://cyber.law.harvard.edu/filtering/china/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hrw.org/reports/2006/china0806/5.htm|title="Race to the Bottom": Corporate Complicity in Chinese Internet Censorship: II. How Censorship Works in China: A Brief Overview|website=www.hrw.org|accessdate=2010-05-24|archive-date=2009-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090901031439/http://www.hrw.org/reports/2006/china0806/5.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>法輪功學員在全球華語媒體世界有組織有媒體地動員對中國官方媒體的反制與挑戰，學者趙月枝認為是最具戲劇張力媒體力量的展現 <ref name="趙月枝2003">{{cite book|author=趙月枝|coauthors=Dr Nick Couldry/ James Curran|title=Contesting Media Power: Alternative Media in a Networked World|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=tiFY59xGHBkC|accessdate=2012-12-20|year=2003|publisher=Rowman & Littlefield|isbn=978-0-7425-2385-2|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315035540/http://books.google.com/books?id=tiFY59xGHBkC|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

另一方面，法輪功學員創辦一系列媒體，如[[大紀元時報|大紀元時報]]、[[新唐人電視台|新唐人電視台]]、[[希望之聲廣播電台|希望之聲廣播電台]]等，不過該等媒體否認其為「法輪功的媒體」，因為該媒體的維護運作是獨立於法輪功之外的。<ref>{{cite news |author=Susan V. Lawrence|title= Falun Gong Adds Media Weapons In Struggle With China's Rulers法輪功學員以媒體對抗中国統治者|work=Wall Street Journal 《[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]》(Eastern edition)|date=2004-04-14 |page=B.2I }}</ref><ref name=Thornton2008>{{cite book |title=Popular Protest in China |last=Thornton |first=Patricia M. |editor=Kevin J. O'Brien |pages=199–200 |chapter=Manufacturing Dissent in Transnational China |publisher=Harvard University Press |isbn=9780674041585 |year=2008 |series=Harvard Contemporary China |volume=15}}</ref><ref name=Tong2015>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=kpHvCgAAQBAJ&pg=RA2-PA71 |page=71 |editor=Jean-Guy A. Goulet |editor2=Liam D. Murphy |editor3=Anastasia Panagakos |last=Tong |first=Clement |title=Religious Diversity Today: Experiencing Religion in the Contemporary World |chapter=Western Apocalyptic Narratives in the International Arena |publisher=ABC-CLIO |year=2015 |isbn=9781440833328 |volume=3 |access-date=2018-01-06 |archive-date=2016-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130103312/https://books.google.com/books?id=kpHvCgAAQBAJ&pg=RA2-PA71 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="James Jiann Hua To, 2014">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=KGe7AwAAQBAJ&pg=PA197 |page=97 |title=Qiaowu: Extra-Territorial Policies for the Overseas Chinese |author=James Jiann Hua To |publisher=Brill |year=2014 |isbn=9789004272286 |access-date=2018-01-06 |archive-date=2016-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130055958/https://books.google.com/books?id=KGe7AwAAQBAJ&pg=PA197 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://dx.doi.org/10.5509/2010832349 |last=Noakes |first=Stephen |title=Falun Gong, Ten Years On |date=June 2010 |journal=Pacific Affairs |volume=83 |number=2 |pages=349–57 |publisher=Pacific Affairs, a division of the University of British Columbia |quote=The Epoch Times newspaper also serves as a mouthpiece for Falun Gong internationally...}}</ref>。{{citation needed|這些媒體稱自己旨在「揭露真相」}}。

2004年，大紀元時報發表《[[九評共產黨|九評共產黨]]》社論，對共產主義和共產黨的政治觀及宇宙觀的評價、對中国共产党歷史的回顧與解讀<ref name=Ping>Hu Ping, "The Falun Gong Phenomenon", in Challenging China: Struggle and Hope in an Era of Change, Sharon Hom and Stacy Mosher (ed) (New York: The New Press, 2007).</ref><ref>Steel, Kevin. 'Revolution number nine', ''The Western Standard'', 11 July 2005.</ref>。這引發了[[三退|退出中国共产党黨組織(三退)]]運動，鼓勵中國公民以化名宣佈退出、放棄他們與共產黨、[[中国共产主义青年团|共青團]]和[[少先隊|少先隊]]的隸屬關係<ref name="auto3">Gutmann, Ethan. ''The Chinese Internet: A dream deferred?''. Testimony given at the National Endowment for Democracy panel discussion "Tiananmen 20 years on", 2 June 2009.</ref>，2011年被俄羅斯智庫評為全球三大重要事件<ref name=RUS>{{cite news|author=安德烈·伊拉里奧諾夫(Андрей Илларионов)|title=「不開玩笑」節目-（公布俄羅斯經濟分析研究院-2011全球十大事件）|url=http://echo.msk.ru/programs/korzun/843403-echo/|newspaper=[[莫斯科迴聲|莫斯科迴聲]]電台|date=2012-01-01|language=ru|accessdate=2016-11-17|archive-date=2016-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313222249/http://echo.msk.ru/programs/korzun/843403-echo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。退黨運動並不訴求要建構何種政治制度，而是從道德基點，剖析共產黨問題。<ref name=UNIAN-1>{{cite news|title=Китайські опозиціонери позитивно оцінюють процес декомунізації в Україні Детальніше читайте на УНІАН(中國異議人士正面評價烏克蘭去共運動)|url=http://press.unian.ua/pressnews/1088271-kitayski-opozitsioneri-pozitivno-otsinyuyut-protses-dekomunizatsiji-v-ukrajini.html|agency=Unian([[烏克蘭獨立新聞社|烏克蘭獨立新聞社]])|date=2015-06-11|accessdate=2016-11-17|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019004628/https://press.unian.ua/pressnews/1088271-kitayski-opozitsioneri-pozitivno-otsinyuyut-protses-dekomunizatsiji-v-ukrajini.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>外媒報導稱，2015年時三退人數逼近2億人<ref name=Speaker2015>{{cite news|title=Why over 1.5 million people a month have been renouncing affiliation with Chinese Communist Party|url=http://thespeaker.co/1-5-million-people-month-renouncing-affiliation-chinese-communist-party/|newspaper=The Speaker《言者》（德國媒體）|quote=〔[http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/15/3/17/n4389139.htm 全文中文編譯]〕|date=2015-03-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402111851/http://thespeaker.co/1-5-million-people-month-renouncing-affiliation-chinese-communist-party/|archivedate=2015-04-02|accessdate=2016-11-17}}</ref>；但外媒於2009年說，退黨網站的數據尚未被獨立核實<ref name="auto3"/>。

美國的法輪功學員，還開發了多款避開中国共产党網路防火牆審查的[[翻牆軟體|翻牆軟體]]，例如[[自由門|自由門]]、[[無界瀏覽|無界瀏覽]]，以協助中國及極權國家的民眾瀏覽網路<ref name="Beiser, Vince 2010">Beiser, Vince. "[http://www.wired.com/2010/11/ff_firewallfighters/ Digital Weapons Help Dissidents Punch Holes in China's Great Firewall] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wired.com/2010/11/ff_firewallfighters/ |date=20201019015818 }}," Wired, 1 November 2010.</ref>。

根據國際司法正義協會(IAFJ)資料，法輪功已經針對最嚴重的國際刑法罪行指控，提出了21世紀最大規模的人權訴訟<ref name=Ownby2008>David Ownby, Falun Gong and the Future of China, 2008</ref>，截至2006年，有54個民事、刑事訴訟正在33個國家進行<ref name=Ownby08future/>。中國以外的法輪功學員，對迫害主要責任人，以[[群體滅絕罪|群體滅絕罪]]和[[反人類罪|反人類罪]]等指控，提出幾十起國際人權訴訟，包括江澤民、[[羅幹|羅幹]]、[[薄熙來|薄熙來]]及其他中國官員<ref>Human Rights Law Foundation, [http://www.hrlf.net/direct.html Direct Litigation] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hrlf.net/direct.html |date=20111111144251 }}. Retrieved 19 March 2011</ref>。儘管其中許多案件，有些法院以主權豁免(sovereign immunity)為理由拒絕裁決；然而，2009年底，西班牙國家法院、阿根廷法庭以[[群體滅絕罪|群體滅絕罪]]和[[反人類罪|反人類罪]]起訴了江澤民、羅幹等高官，並要求逮捕他們；不過這裁決很大程度上是象徵性的，難以被實現。西班牙法院還起訴了薄熙來、賈慶林和吳官正。<ref name=elmundo>{{cite web|url=http://www.elmundo.es/elmundo/2009/11/14/espana/1258230601.html|title=La Audiencia pide interrogar al ex presidente chino Jiang por genocidio - España - elmundo.es|first=Unidad Editorial|last=Internet|website=www.elmundo.es|accessdate=2012-04-13|archive-date=2016-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025083959/http://www.elmundo.es/elmundo/2009/11/14/espana/1258230601.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=spanish>Charlotte Cuthbertson, (15 Nov 2009) [http://www.theepochtimes.com/n2/world/spain-court-falun-gong-genocide-jiang-zemin-25211.html "Spanish Judge Calls Top Chinese Officials to Account for Genocide"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theepochtimes.com/n2/world/spain-court-falun-gong-genocide-jiang-zemin-25211.html |date=20120704142507 }}, ''The Epoch Times''</ref><ref>Luis Andres Henao, [http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/12/23/us-argentina-china-falungong-idUSTRE5BM02B20091223 Argentine judge asks China arrests over Falun Gong] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/12/23/us-argentina-china-falungong-idUSTRE5BM02B20091223 |date=20151203212405 }}, 22 December 2009</ref><ref name=ArgentinaJudge>[http://www.faluninfo.net/article/935/?cid=82 Argentine Judge Orders Arrest of Top Chinese Communist Party Officials for Crimes Against Humanity] {{Wayback|url=http://www.faluninfo.net/article/935/?cid=82 |date=20110925154535 }} 20 December 2009</ref>

