|accessdate=2017-02-02|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201024018/https://foreignpolicyblogs.com/2016/05/09/chinese-government-front-groups-act-violation-u-s-law/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

