 Times’ reporting is balanced; a slight right-wing bias is mostly displayed via story choice.|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130022022/https://www.allsides.com/news-source/epoch-times-media-bias|dead-url=no}}</ref>AllSides 2020年11月底專文調查比較幾家媒體的傾向，調查顯示多數看法認為大紀元中立、美聯社AP中立、BBC偏左派、[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]偏左派或左派、彭博社偏左派。<ref name="AllSides2">{{Cite news|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124190025/https://www.allsides.com/blog/how-readers-rated-media-bias-ap-bbc-and-epoch-times-and-more |date=2020-11-23|title=How Readers Rated the Media Bias of AP, BBC and The Epoch Times, and More|work=AllSides Media Bias Ratings|language=en-US|quote=}}</ref>
